org.teatrove.trove.util
Class DecimalConvertor.LargeUInt

java.lang.Object
  org.teatrove.trove.util.DecimalConvertor.LargeUInt
Enclosing class:
DecimalConvertor
public static final class DecimalConvertor.LargeUInt
extends Object

Mutable large unsigned integer class, similar to BigInteger, but specialized. The set of operations is limited to those needed for converting binary floating point numbers to decimal.

Version:
Author:
Brian S O'Neill

divideClose

public int divideClose(DecimalConvertor.LargeUInt v)
                throws ArithmeticException
Divide this LargeUInt by v, storing the remainder in this and returning the quotient. This method assumes that (this / v) is very small, less than 10. If the ratio is larger, performance degrades.
